                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 22160.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">King</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bangkok</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1909-11-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 1, 1909</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Minister King says he has been asked by British court to act as executor in will
                    of deceased British subject and asks instructions.</p>
            </div>
